sources.description:
When the world falls apart, survival becomes the ultimate test!
A deputy sheriff stops motorists on a mountain road after police dispatch reports of a possible nuclear attack.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/wOBT7wr-Ky4


Original title: This Is Not a Test (1962)
This film is subtitled in many languages

Director: Fredric Gadette
Writers: Peter Abenheim, Betty Laskey, Fredric Gadette
Stars: Seamon Glass, Thayer Roberts, Aubrey Martin
Genres: Classics, Drama, Sci-Fi
